{
  "title": "BD Pyxis MedStation — Connected Fleet",
  "description": "Pyxis MedStation ES live IoT telemetry: cabinet health, drawer/cubie mechanics, dispensing workflow, BD Pharmogistics inventory sync, controlled-substance compliance, and the pyxis-inventory-api / pharmacy-ehr-bridge cascade view used for BitsSRE root-cause walks.",
