    {
      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "# BD Pyxis MedStation ES — Live Fleet\n**Manufacturer:** Becton Dickinson · **Model:** MedStation ES · **Firmware:** 1.6.6\n\nAll metrics filter on `device_type:pyxis_medstation` and `device_manufacturer:BD`. Use the template variables to scope by floor / wing / department.",
